{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_01","textHome":"我的名字是土岐沙绪。尽管不至于像时女村落@那个程度，但我也是出身于乡下，对城市不@太熟悉。你能为我解答很多我感到困惑的地@方的话，就帮大忙了。不过，我没有什么能@拿来回谢的呢…。啊，可以的话请享用乡村@菜哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_18","textHome":"为了别的谁而帮忙其实也是为了自己。因为，@大家能被治愈而得到幸福，就是对我的欣慰@了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":102700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_19","textHome":"我不去看未来…我会回首过去，将其化为我的@力量!!"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":102700}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_20","textHome":"如果我的成长，能够促成时女罪恶的旧习的革@除，我会非常开心的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_21","textHome":"千儿和静香都接纳了罪孽深重的我。所以我想@为了她们二人贡献自己的力量的心情，可以@说更甚于为了村里"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":102700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":102700,"motion":1}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_22","textHome":"在参与进时女村落的黑暗之后，我绝无可能被@原谅了。但是…所以，我会为了不让历史重@演而努力！为了不让和我一样的人出现，实@现一个健全地魔法少女村落而努力！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":102700,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_00_23","textHome":"我们所决心要实现的魔法少女的和平与为了日@出之国战国即便出现了动摇，我也会为了拯@救大家，继续使用这份力量。小的沟壑不去@填补，就会随着时间就会扩大，变得无法修@复了啊…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":102700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102702,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1027_02_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":102702,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":102702,"motion":3